MPS demo project (MPS 2.5.1)

Steps to open the project in MPS:
1. clone the repository
2. start MPS
3. open the project through the STM.mpr project file
4. In the "Project View" panel on the left hand side of the screen select the four language nodes (icons with capital letter L), right-click and choose "Rebuild Selected Modules"
5. Select the two solution nodes (icons with capital letter S), right-click and choose "Rebuild Selected Modules"
6. Now you should be able to run the solutions in the STM_sandbox module as well as create your own ones
